13.10(a) PI CONTROLLER TUNING USING THE  AUTO TUNE VARIATION “ATV” METHOD  |POLVER05_0 |1
d(T)/d(t) =  (WC*(Ti-T)+q)/rhoVCp 
d(T0)/d(t) =  (T-T0-(taud/2)*dTdt)*2/taud 
d(Tm)/d(t) =  (T0-Tm)/taum 
d(errsum)/d(t) =  Tr-Tm 
WC =  500 
rhoVCp =  4000 
taud =  1 
taum =  5 
Tr =  80
Ti =  60 
Kc = 0
error=Tr-Tm 
relay=if(error<0)then(-1)else(1)
q =  10000+relay*4000
dTdt =  (WC*(Ti-T)+q)/rhoVCp 
t(0)=0
T(0)=80
T0(0)=80
Tm(0)=80
errsum(0)=0
t(f)=100


